message: Hi Bob, I'm offering you a great deal on this product. I think you'll find it very valuable. I'm willing to part with it for $118.
Thanks for the offer, Alice. I appreciate you considering my budget. I'm looking to spend closer to $105. Would you be willing to work with me on that?
Thanks for the offer, Bob.  I understand your position, but $105 is a bit too low for me. How about we meet in the middle at $111?
